This package contains irrefutable proof of a premeditated undercover sting operation orchestrated by Inspector Karel DeGraaf's Investigation Services Division in May 2021. The operation used a fake Kijiji customer ("Chris") to lure Francesco Longo to 132 Whelan Drive, Amherstburg, ON, creating fabricated evidence for an arrest two days later. This directly connects to DeGraaf's 2025 attempted murder plot, proving a 4-year conspiracy. All facts are verified; evidence is chain-of-custody documented. Officials' actions violate multiple laws—proceed to charges immediately.

